<div class="detail"><ul class="info"><li class=" first"><a class="num" rel="nofollow" href="news/2020/08/reaction_sony_wants_ps5_to_be_the_best_place_to_play_and_itll_open_its_wallet_to_achieve_it#comment5747955">3</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="username accent" title="Ralizah" href="/users/Ralizah">Ralizah</a></li><li class=" last"><time class="date age " datetime="2020-08-04T14:02:25+00:00"><span>Tue 4th Aug 2020</span></time></li></ul>
<section class="text">
<p>Moneyhatting developers to keep games off of other consoles for a period of time always sucks, no matter who does it. Besides, in the end, timed exclusivity doesn't dramatically change the library of a console.</p>
<p>If PS5 turns into the home console space equivalent of the EGS, I might have to re-evaluate my support for them.</p>
</section>
